Reminder - Hudson Global (HSON) Goes Ex-Dividend Soon
Looking at the universe of stocks we cover at Dividend Channel, on 6/10/16, Hudson Global Inc will trade ex-dividend, for its quarterly dividend of $0.05, payable on 6/24/16. As a percentage of HSON's recent stock price of $2.19, this dividend works out to approximately 2.28%, so look for shares of Hudson Global Inc to trade 2.28% lower — all else being equal — when HSON shares open for trading on 6/10/16.

