Hudson Global Inc.


            
            Hudson Global, Inc. engages in the provision of professional-level recruitment and talent solutions. It includes Permanent Recruitment, Temporary Contracting, Recruitment Process Outsourcing (RPO), and Talent Management Solutions. It operates through the following geographical segments: Hudson Americas, Hudson Asia Pacific, and Hudson Europe. The company was founded on March 14, 2003 and is headquartered in New York, NY.

            
